The Fall Guys Beta will run for several weeks and will consist of a series of playtests that help us at Mediatonic gain vital feedback on the game we've built so far. 

 Please bear in mind that Fall Guys is still in development so expect some hiccups and downtime along the way! 

 Don't forget to join the official Fall Guys Discord to get involved - we can't wait to hear what you have to say.    

 Fall Guys launches later in 2020!  
 Love, Mediatonic.
